     __________________________________________________________________

                            MLS-related Publications

      This page (http://mls.jpl.nasa.gov/joe/um_pubs.html) maintained by Joe
      Waters (joe@mls.jpl.nasa.gov). Last updated 7 Dec 2001.

   Listed here are peer-reviewed scientific publications which include use
   of MLS data, have directly contributed to development and validation of
   the experiments (including related aircraft and balloon experiments)
   and/or their data, or have been produced by members of the MLS Science
   Team as part of their scientific research associated with the MLS
   experiment. The publications are grouped by year, and then in
   alphabetical order of first author. (Also, the book How Soon is Now?
   The Truth about the Ozone Hole by Nicholas Booth [Simon & Schuster,
   1994] gives a lively non-technical account of developments related to
   our current understanding of stratospheric ozone depletion, and
   mentions some contributions from MLS.)
     * 2001: published or in press to date
     * Papers submitted and currently in review
     * 2000 publications
     * 1999 publications
     * 1998 publications
     * 1997 publications
     * 1996 publications
     * 1995 publications
     * 1994 publications
     * 1993 publications
     * 1992 and earlier publications
     __________________________________________________________________

